<HEADLINE>
FT  27 NOV 93 / London Tube appeals abroad for cable help
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By ANDREW BAXTER and CHARLES BATCHELOR
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
London Underground yesterday appealed for technical help from big UK cable
manufacturers and international subway train operators to repair its
